data.eml:eml: Chronicle of Nature - Phenology of Arachnids of Kondinskie Lakes National Park named after L. F. Stashkevich

Arachnids Phenology dataset compiled in the context of Chronicle of Nature program in Kondinskie Lakes National Park named after L. F. Stashkevich (Russian Federation) consisting of 8 records collected during 8 years between 2001 and 2008.
